==== Download Zoom ====

+ sudo su
+ cd /usr/local/src/
+ wget https://zoom.us/client/latest/zoom_amd64.deb

==== Instalasi Zoom ====

+ sudo su
+ sudo apt -y install gdebi libxcb-xtest0 libgl1-mesa-glx libegl1-mesa libxcb-xinerama0
+ cd /usr/local/src
+ dpkg -i zoom_amd64.deb

==== Thank you very much :) ====
